    <div class="feat-list">
        <h3 class="stnd">Core Capabilities</h3>
        
        <div class="list-item">
            <a href="#" rel="feature-desc-1" class="img-frame pngbg"><span class="btn-enlarge pngbg"></span></a>
            <div class="list-img"><img src="/images/product/R2-assist-sm.png" width="217" height="147" border="0" alt="" /></div>
            <h4>Code Assist</h4>
            <p>
              Quick access to Ruby, HTML, CSS and JavaScript structures, methods, elements, properties, tags & attributes. Helpful information about the
              element also shown. Supports your custom code as well.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div id="feature-desc-1" style="display: none;">
            <img src="/images/product/R2-assist-lrg.png" width="585" height="383" border="0" alt="" />
            <h5>Code Assist</h5>
            <p>
              Quick access to Ruby, HTML, CSS and JavaScript structures, methods, elements, properties, tags & attributes. Helpful information about the
              element also shown. Supports your custom code as well.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        
        <div class="list-item">
            <a href="#" rel="feature-desc-2" class="img-frame pngbg"><span class="btn-enlarge pngbg"></span></a>
            <div class="list-img"><img src="/images/product/R2-debug-sm.png" width="217" height="147" border="0" alt="" /></div>
            <h4>Integrated Debugger</h4>
            <p>
                Set breakpoints, inspect variables, control execution. The integrated Ruby & Rails debugger helps you squash those bugs.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div id="feature-desc-2" style="display: none;">
            <img src="/images/product/R2-debug-lrg.png" width="585" height="383" border="0" alt="" />
            <h5>Integrated Debugger</h5>
            <p>
                Set breakpoints, inspect variables, control execution. The integrated Ruby & Rails debugger helps you squash those bugs.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        
        <div class="list-item list-item-last">
            <a href="#" rel="feature-desc-3" class="img-frame pngbg"><span class="btn-enlarge pngbg"></span></a>
            <div class="list-img"><img src="/images/product/R2-colors-sm.png" width="217" height="147" border="0" alt="" /></div>
            <h4>Syntax Coloring</h4>
            <p>
                Customize syntax highlighting by colorizing various types of code and data types in your editors.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div id="feature-desc-3" style="display: none;">
            <img src="/images/product/R2-colors-lrg.png" width="585" height="383" border="0" alt="" />
            <h5>Syntax Coloring</h5>
            <p>
                Customize syntax highlighting by colorizing various types of code and data types in your editors.
            </p>
        </div>

        
        
        <div class="cf"></div>
        
        <div class="list-item">
            <a href="#" rel="feature-desc-4" class="img-frame pngbg"><span class="btn-enlarge pngbg"></span></a>
            <div class="list-img"><img src="/images/product/R2-outline-sm.png" width="217" height="147" border="0" alt="" /></div>
            <h4>Outlining</h4>
            <p>
                View and navigate the structures in your file using this hierarchical outline of your Ruby or HTML page.
                Select nodes to jump to that location in the editor. Filter nodes to see collections that match patterns. 
            </p>
        </div>
        <div id="feature-desc-4" style="display: none;">
            <img src="/images/product/R2-outline-lrg.png" width="585" height="383" border="0" alt="" />
            <h5>Outlining</h5>
            <p>
                View and navigate the structures in your file using this hierarchical outline of your Ruby or HTML page.
                Select nodes to jump to that location in the editor. Filter nodes to see collections that match patterns. 
            </p>
        </div>
        
        
        <div class="list-item">
            <a href="#" rel="feature-desc-5" class="img-frame pngbg"><span class="btn-enlarge pngbg"></span></a>
            <div class="list-img"><img src="/images/product/R2-search-sm.png" width="217" height="147" border="0" alt="" /></div>
            <h4>Powerful Search</h4>
            <p>
                Flexible search tools help you quickly pinpoint patterns across one or multiple projects to find exactly what you need.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div id="feature-desc-5" style="display: none;">
            <img src="/images/product/R2-search-lrg.png" width="585" height="383" border="0" alt="" />
            <h5>Powerful Search</h5>
            <p>
                Flexible search tools help you quickly pinpoint patterns across one or multiple projects to find exactly what you need.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="list-item list-item-last">
            <a href="#" rel="feature-desc-6" class="img-frame pngbg"><span class="btn-enlarge pngbg"></span></a>
            <div class="list-img"><img src="/images/product/R2-rubyviews-sm.png" width="217" height="147" border="0" alt="" /></div>
            <h4>Ruby-Specific Views</h4>
            <p>
                Ruby and Rails introduce unique facilities and tools such as generators, rake, gems, RI, rdocs & plugins. RadRails includes
                specialized views to access these unique Ruby features.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div id="feature-desc-6" style="display: none;">
            <img src="/images/product/R2-rubyviews-lrg.png" width="585" height="383" border="0" alt="" />
            <h5>Ruby-Specific Views</h5>
            <p>
                Ruby and Rails introduce unique facilities and tools such as generators, rake, gems, RI, rdocs & plugins. RadRails includes
                specialized views to access these unique Ruby features.
            </p>
        </div>        
     
